          <li><b>Language:</b> English, pidgin (a blend of English, Hawaiian, Japanese and Portuguese)</li>
          <li><b>Flight time:</b> Sydney 9 hours, 45 minutes; Melbourne 10 hours 30 minutes; Brisbane 9 hours 30 minutes</li>
          <li><b>Getting around:</b> Car, bike, taxi or trolley</li>
        </ul>
